WEBVTT

00:04.214 --> 00:06.216
[theme music playing]

00:14.933 --> 00:17.101
[Maria] <i>I'm a pterodactyl.</i>

00:20.939 --> 00:22.065
[Bruce playing drums] Da, da.

00:22.148 --> 00:24.776
Da, da... Daddy never loved me.

00:24.859 --> 00:26.653
-Da, da, da...
-[knocking]

00:26.736 --> 00:28.071
-Maria. [chuckling]
-Hey.

00:28.154 --> 00:30.114
To what do I owe this gorgeous surprise?

00:30.198 --> 00:32.992
Well, I've just come in
to pick up my check.

00:33.076 --> 00:35.328
Ah! That's strange.

00:35.411 --> 00:37.080
You should have received that moons ago.

00:37.163 --> 00:39.457
