about the money...

00:39.541 --> 00:40.917
it's just tight right now.

00:41.000 --> 00:43.711
If you hadn't slept through
the table read of <i>Ghostbrides,</i>

00:43.795 --> 00:45.129
you'd have two checks.

00:45.213 --> 00:46.214
[groaning]

00:49.133 --> 00:51.344
