01:31.467 --> 01:33.011
Hello, Admiral.

01:34.012 --> 01:35.388
What do you enjoy?

01:35.471 --> 01:37.890
Do you have sports or...

01:37.974 --> 01:39.684
[inhales deeply]

01:39.767 --> 01:40.977
[razzes]

01:41.060 --> 01:43.730
[inhales deeply and blows raspberry]

01:45.481 --> 01:46.608
