01:49.402 --> 01:54.449
Look, I choose to do good
in the world in my daily life.

01:54.532 --> 01:55.742
One-on-one.

01:55.825 --> 01:57.452
Your picture's in the brochure.

01:57.535 --> 01:59.037
Goddamn it, Bruce.

01:59.120 --> 02:02.040
